    "Distribute and assign the different household tasks. This way, you will avoid arguments as much as possible. Leaving it to each person's goodwill does not work." : {
      "comment" : "PDF house rule 1",
      "localizations" : {
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Distribuye y asigna las diferentes tareas del hogar. Así evitarás discusiones en la medida de lo posible. Dejarlo a la buena voluntad de cada uno no funciona."
          }
        }
      }
    },
